weekly_modifiers.description: Boss enemies have 40% more health and inflict up to 15% increased damage.

weekly_modifiers.name: Raging

weekly_modifiers.name: Volcanic
weekly_modifiers.description: While in combat, enemies periodically cause gouts of flame to erupt beneath the feet of distant players.

weekly_modifiers.name: Reaping
weekly_modifiers.description: Non-boss enemies are empowered by Bwonsamdi and periodically seek vengeance from beyond the grave.
